{"type":null,"faqId":11327,"title":"Mate2 (MT2-L05)   WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">设置</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">无线和网络</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> </span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">&gt; <b>WLAN</b></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">，再点击菜单键并进入<b>高级</b></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">在休眠状态下保持</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">WLAN</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">连接</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">，设置为</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">始终</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32329\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">个选项的含义如下：</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">始终</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">：一直保持</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">的连接。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">仅限充电时</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">分钟断开连接。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">从不</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">分钟断开连接。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2087","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398218607000,"seriesProductName":"MT2-L05","visitedTimes":16,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Mate2 (MT2-L05)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}